# @hive/{{name}}

gRPC domain package for the {{pascalCase name}} domain. Provides proto definitions, generated TypeScript types, gRPC client, and DTOs for the API gateway and other services.

## Usage

```typescript
import { Hive{{pascalCase name}}ClientService } from '@hive/{{name}}';
```

## Development

```bash
# Regenerate TypeScript types from proto files
pnpm gen

# Build
pnpm build

# Run tests
pnpm test
```

## Adding a new resource

Run the scaffold tool from `the-hive-nest/`:

```bash
pnpm scaffold --resource MyResource --package {{name}} --service {{constantCase name}}_SERVICE_NAME
```
